  "detailed_description": "<h1>Roadmap</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/63fdf9d52b55628b3e218aa764ee3f5d.poster.avif?t=1771277863\" width=616 height=902 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/63fdf9d52b55628b3e218aa764ee3f5d.webm?t=1771277863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/63fdf9d52b55628b3e218aa764ee3f5d.mp4?t=1771277863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >the Earth has become uninhabitable.<br><br>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/0ec3bc37a2fa56657f24165536d1137a.avif?t=1771277863\" width=616 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been hired by the bunker managers. It's your only chance. Don't screw it up or you'll be kicked out of the bunker. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/7de9571c54ccddb14266cd227ce81cef.avif?t=1771277863\" width=616 height=266 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/5fab205f3f0f16a5f2d1470fef5df9bd.avif?t=1771277863\" width=616 height=128 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/49413ba66a1894f44427b273b5f221cb.avif?t=1771277863\" width=512 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >your job is to fix the problems of the bunkers and make sure they stand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/68833e6bab7456edec6b5f3d1326d1f7.avif?t=1771277863\" width=512 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The creatures are causing problems in the bunker. their life sources are becoming unusable, find them and make them work. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/4ef5041093dbe006bba02bf34076a996.poster.avif?t=1771277863\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/4ef5041093dbe006bba02bf34076a996.webm?t=1771277863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/4ef5041093dbe006bba02bf34076a996.mp4?t=1771277863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/581fd96bbd896c032a2e72f9d98f4548.avif?t=1771277863\" width=512 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >you have to be careful that this bunker doesn't turn out to be a grave instead of a chance. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/23f6b4bdc08bad0140160b802df5387e.poster.avif?t=1771277863\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/23f6b4bdc08bad0140160b802df5387e.webm?t=1771277863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/23f6b4bdc08bad0140160b802df5387e.mp4?t=1771277863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/d31257ddb26235ce2bb83f27a7f34e97.avif?t=1771277863\" width=512 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>On the 3rd day, the managers expect you to complete the service charge or it will be your last day in the bunker.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/8a6c22ac21d32fb44fd57e39cf7864c9.poster.avif?t=1771277863\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/8a6c22ac21d32fb44fd57e39cf7864c9.webm?t=1771277863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/8a6c22ac21d32fb44fd57e39cf7864c9.mp4?t=1771277863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/92162d2186b856353075aefb42613373.avif?t=1771277863\" width=512 height=64 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >in-game voice chat.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >silly animated characters.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >engines in need of repair</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >procedural map.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >tools you can use.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >horrible monsters.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >interact with bunker NPCs.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2-6 player online coop</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/f807784985db586acc93986d43a00987.avif?t=1771277863\" width=512 height=64 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/2ebd355f713381e272c1d7775dde9e3f.poster.avif?t=1771277863\" width=616 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/2ebd355f713381e272c1d7775dde9e3f.webm?t=1771277863\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2780470/extras/2ebd355f713381e272c1d7775dde9e3f.mp4?t=1771277863\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
